    "DefaultText": "Ore Sluice"
  },
  "CardDescription": {
    "ParentObjectID": "water_sawmill_ore_sluice_placed",
    "LocalizationKey": "Water_Sawmill_OreSluicePlaced_CardDescription",
    "DefaultText": "A water-powered sluice box for washing soil and separating mineral deposits. Load mud piles, dirt piles, or fine dirt, then run the sluice to process them for greenstone, flint, stone, and occasionally metal nuggets."
  },
  "CardHelpSection": {
    "ParentObjectID": "water_sawmill_ore_sluice_placed",
    "LocalizationKey": "Water_Sawmill_OreSluicePlaced_CardHelpSection",
    "DefaultText": "<b>Operation:</b> Load mud piles, dirt piles, or fine dirt into the sluice, then press Sluice All. Each drop is rolled independently — a single pile can yield multiple items or nothing.\n\nDrop chances (Mud / Dirt / Fine Dirt):\nIron Nugget: 8% / 5% / 1%\nCopper Nugget: 12% / 8% / 1%\nTin Nugget: 8% / 5% / 1%\nGreenstone: 22% / 18% / 12%\nFlint: 30% / 20% / 10%\nStone: 55% / 40% / 10%\nClay: 10% / 20% / 55%\n\nNuggets spawn at 35% quality."
  },
